No, the reason they put the mute function in while scanning is because
most people couldn&#39;t stand the &quot;bleep-blop-bloop&quot; while the radio
scanned without the mute.

Then again, there&#39;s Imaginary Landscape # 4 by John Cage ...
:-)

Zack


